data.chText: 碍眼的建筑；丑陋的东西；令人厌恶的东西
data.enText: a building, an object, etc. that is unpleasant to look at
That old factory is a real eyesore!

value.def: You describe a building or place as an eyesore when it is extremely ugly and you dislike it or disapprove of it.

example.ex: Poverty leads to slums, which are an eyesore and a health hazard.
example.tran: 贫困产生了贫民窟，那里不仅有碍观瞻，而且卫生隐患严重。

value.tran: 碍眼的东西（如建筑物等）
